          h2 Privacy Policy
          p
            | #[i Effective July 26th, 2018]
            br
            |Your privacy is important to Halcyon Biotechnologies, Inc. (Halcyon). To best protect your privacy, we are providing this notice here explaining our online information usage practices and what choices you have about how your information is collected and then used.
